_sText:
This is the start of a series of maps I am going to make. All of which will be just thrown together, they won't have any specific layout, i'll just add stuff as I go through making the map until I'm happy with it, at which time I will submit it as a map to download. 

This one is full of places to go and many ways to get there. It is almost perfectly symetical so the teamplay is excellent.

Hope you enjoy it!
